data.title: Area 51 in movies and TV
data.meta_description: In year of release order. From 2024 going back in time to 1995.
data.text:
AREA 51 HAS GONE DARK DURING AN OFF SCHEDULE VISIT FROM THE PRESIDENT. IT'S UP TO A TEAM OF WILD MERCENARIES TO FIGURE OUT WHAT HAS HAPPENED, WHERE THE 500 EMPLOYEES OF THE BASE HAVE GONE, AND TO RESCUE THE PRESIDENT FROM A SUPERNATURAL FORCE THAT HAS IT UNDER CONTROL.

A meme is not born out of thin air. The rest is history - but due to organized government propaganda - not the true history. Social engineering and weaponized social media enabled a manufactured consent - disinformation is alive and well.

An alien-obsessed podcaster and his friends travel to AREA 51 and find themselves on the run and on the menu in the deadly no-man's land outside the base.

Area 51 is yet again witness to the worlds most sinister conspiracy plot when an alien Swamp monster runs amok, killing all in its wake, with a paranoid scientist, two stoned security guards and the FBI hot on its trail.

2 children help their alien friend get to his spaceship in Area 51. A Short film made in unreal engine in 48 hours for the 2023 Vancouver 48 film fest.

An outbreak occurs in the infamous Area 51 leading a group of survivors to an underground bunker.. only to learn.. they are not alone.

A shapeshifting alien from outer space terrorizes a town near Area 51. The extraterrestrials feast on human brains and decapitate people. They have secretly lived on Earth for millions of years.

Sheera, a sexy alien warrior uses a power glitch to escape from captivity at Area 51. Now she must elude her enemies to rescue Kyra, her fellow warrior, and find her way home.

In 2013 the CIA declassified documents that acknowledged the existence of Area 51. Six years later, millions responded to an internet post advocating to storm the gates. Why does this Top-Secret location continue to draw so much attention?

Olivia Saint-Cloud is a reporter for a new start up company. Seeking a big new story to take her to the top, she learns of Michael a ordinary American who seemingly kidnapped an alien from Area 51 and has gone missing. Olivia now with aide from her cameraman Oliver, sets out to uncover the story.

Even today scientists are baffled by the geometric perfection of the egyptian pyramids and the newly discovered Gobekli Tepe. The truth is stranger than fiction. Seek the truth with Wilbur's Conspiracy Theories: Area 51 Revealed.

Get ready as the dynamic duo turn on the TV and get tuned into a viral saga that takes them deep into the world of Area 51. Combining new footage with re-dubbed sci-fi cinema, this is the wackiest coronasploitation comedy yet.

Joe and Emmett Hayes head to Nevada desert to observe, investigate and embrace the pandemonium of storming Area 51. And, they dive into the history of the facility.

Here it is - the Top Secret Area 51 video that #UFOLove was able to procure with his prodigious hacking skills. We find out everything we want to know about the origin of Clorg on the earth.
